author: bpendleton
msg: DERBY-4288: Tools guide lists too many parameters for SYSCS_EXPORT_QUERY procs
The manual page for the export query procedures in the Tools guide had an
incorrect extra 'tablename' parameter for the SYSCS_EXPORT_QUERY and
SYSCS_EXPORT_QUERY_LOBS_TO_EXTFILE procedures. This change simply removes
that parameter from the syntax diagrams.
